{"type": "article", "id": 16566, "title": "Chuck Taylor All Star ‘70 太空系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-26T06:51:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 49, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122439qib5o0fr82K43Nhv.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是 First String 推出的 Chuck Taylor All Star ‘70 太空系列，以 1970 年代经典的  Converse 鞋为蓝本，加入那个年代狂热的太空漫游的主题。黑白款直接从宇航员的衣服样式提取灵感，而米色圆圈款型源于打开的降落伞，在流行样式中显得与众不同。近期会在门店销售，定价 120 美元。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143804xLT9sf8UlaG2ZwKt.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143806cqo9KGwb8gv3LRQm.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143806XbRMKdmEy564QaL8.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143806Mb2RwlhN8V7KLP1k.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143807XhW30UQEsSxIuMlJ.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}